title: What Are the Biggest Unsolved Mysteries From the Trade Deadline? | The Answer
description:
Chris is joined by Justin Verrier and Rob Mahoney to dive into some of the greatest unsolved mysteries from the trade deadline and look back at the moves made by the Nuggets, Bulls, Heat, and more.

Guests: Rob Mahoney and Justin Verrier
